[center]
[b]
[color=green]CodeLifter[/color] is a source code viewer that lets you see all of the code on any http:// html page, including pages protected by no-right-click scripts, trapped in windows without file menus or url boxes, and 'referrer' pages that cannot be seen in your browser. You can also access .css (cascading style sheet) scripts, external .js files (JavaScript files), and any other text file at an http:// address.

[img]http://www.codelifter.com/screenshots/codelifter557x405.gif[/img]

[color=blue]System requirements:[/color]
Windows 95/98/Me/NT/2000/XP/Vista/Windows7
Download and install to try; click lower right question ? mark to register
[/b][/center]

[b][url="http://www.codelifter.com/faq/faq.html"]FaQ[/url] [/b]

Registration:[/color]

1- Install CL5001
2- Open Application
3- Open Keygen
4- Klick on (?) in the bottom right of the CodeLifter
5- copy the serial number 
past it into the keygen and then copy the key and past it into the Codelifter
add any email and hit register and it's done
